OL,4,CSEND family spends #20k fighting for
OL,5,Cschool place
OL,6, Parents of children with special
OL,7, educational needs and disabilities
OL,8, (SEND) say they are struggling to
OL,9, secure suitable school places for them.
OL,11,FAnna Geldard spent #20,000 fighting for
OL,12,Fthe Education, Health and Social Care
OL,13,FPlan (EHCP) her child is entitled to.
OL,15,FShe said it was "so stressful" and the
OL,16,Femotional impact was far greater than
OL,17,Feven the financial cost to her family.
OL,19,FThe government said the SEND system was
OL,20,Funder review and it had also increased
OL,21,FSEND funding to #8bn in 2021-22.
